content: LOL. I almost thought you were serious with that for a second. Realize you were probably just trolling. Nobody could be THAT stupid. Well maybe a rank and file Democrat but not anyone with a brain for sure.
Look go beat up your wife or something

And just in case any poorly informed people read your tweet. There is no such Senator as Thurman. It was Strom Thurmond and he DID switch parties. Robert Byrd, KKK member and Democrat remained an honored Democrat until his death.
